# Demo mode — flip the briefing UI into canned-mock content for
# screenshots, video recordings, or showcase demos without needing
# a real Postgres + LLM provider chain.
#
# When set:
#   - /api/onboarding/status returns ready + default seats (no wizard bounce)
#   - /api/briefing GET returns the ROLE_DATA mock with isExample=true
#   - /api/briefing POST returns a random mock answer (no metric_refresh job)
#
# The NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix lets both server and client code read the flag.
# Copy this file to apps/web/.env.local and uncomment the line below to enable.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_DEMO=true
